msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Panel"

msgid "Logout"
msgstr "Wyloguj"

msgid "Login"
msgstr "Zaloguj"

msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "Zaczynaj"

msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Kontakt"

msgid "Learn smarter, not harder."
msgstr "Ucz sie madrzej, nie ciezej."

msgid "The smarter way to study"
msgstr "Sprytniejszy sposob nauki"

msgid "Master any subject"
msgstr "Opanuj dowolny temat"

msgid "at your own pace"
msgstr "we wlasnym tempie"

msgid "Create custom word lists with flexible study fields. Study with flashcards,"
msgstr "Tworz wlasne listy slow z elastycznymi polami. Ucz sie z fiszkami,"

msgid "track your progress, and actually remember what you learn."
msgstr "sledz postepy i naprawde zapamietuj to, czego sie uczysz."

msgid "Start for free"
msgstr "Zacznij za darmo"

msgid "Definition"
msgstr "Definicja"

msgid "Lasting for a very short time"
msgstr "Trwajace bardzo krotko"

msgid "The ephemeral beauty of cherry blossoms"
msgstr "Ulotne piekno kwitnacych wisni"

msgid "Everything you need to study effectively"
msgstr "Wszystko, czego potrzebujesz do skutecznej nauki"

msgid "Custom Study Lists"
msgstr "Wlasne listy nauki"

msgid "Create word lists tailored to any subject — vocabulary, formulas, dates, concepts."
msgstr "Tworz listy slow dopasowane do kazdego tematu — slownictwo, wzory, daty, pojecia."

msgid "Flexible Fields"
msgstr "Elastyczne pola"

msgid "Add as many fields as you need per word: description, examples, notes, and more."
msgstr "Dodaj tyle pol, ile potrzebujesz: opis, przyklady, notatki i wiecej."

msgid "Fast & Simple"
msgstr "Szybko i prosto"

msgid "A clean interface that gets out of your way so you can focus on learning."
msgstr "Przejrzysty interfejs, ktory pozwala skupic sie na nauce."

msgid "Have a question or feedback? We would love to hear from you."
msgstr "Masz pytanie lub opinie? Chetnie Cie wysluchamy."

msgid "We usually reply within 24 hours."
msgstr "Zwykle odpowiadamy w ciagu 24 godzin."

msgid "Back to home"
msgstr "Powrot do strony glownej"

msgid "Sign in"
msgstr "Zaloguj sie"

msgid "Please log in to continue."
msgstr "Zaloguj sie, aby kontynuowac."

msgid "Quiz Complete!"
msgstr "Quiz zakonczony!"

msgid "Your score"
msgstr "Twoj wynik"

msgid "Excellent work!"
msgstr "Swietna robota!"

msgid "Good job!"
msgstr "Dobra robota!"

msgid "Keep practicing!"
msgstr "Cwicz dalej!"

msgid "Try Again"
msgstr "Sprobuj ponownie"

msgid "Back to Dashboard"
msgstr "Powrot do panelu"
